				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\mathbf{B}$$\end{document}). This design was developed to improve measurements of Saturn’s strong magnetic field.

