				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$B=\mathrm {constant}$$\end{document}. A related example of such behavior occurs if the amplitude δB⊥/B0\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
